Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:19.61,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}注视着你 Red eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:24.28,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}一直在寻找真理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:28.62,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}却在彷徨中迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:35.21,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1300)\blur3\be3}万亿种元素 编织成天罗地网
