Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:42.26,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}简直太混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:44.30,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}灵魂伤痛 永不磨灭
